ale]]\n|2\n|50,251\n|4\n|561.2\n|90\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Dallas County, Alabama|Dallas]]\n|7\n|43,820\n|16\n|978.7\n|45\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[DeKalb County, Alabama|DeKalb]]\n|14\n|71,109\n|20\n|777.1\n|92\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Elmore County, Alabama|Elmore]]\n|19\n|79,303\n|24\n|618.5\n|128\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Escambia County, Alabama|Escambia]]\n|3\n|38,319\n|8\n|945.1\n|41\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Etowah County, Alabama|Etowah]]\n|36\n|104,430\n|34\n|535.0\n|195\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Fayette County, Alabama|Fayette]]\n|1\n|17,241\n|6\n|627.7\n|27\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Franklin County, Alabama|Franklin]]\n|6\n|31,704\n|19\n|633.8\n|50\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Geneva County, Alabama|Geneva]]\n|0\n|26,790\n|0\n|574.4\n|47\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Greene County, Alabama|Greene]]\n|6\n|9,045\n|66\n|647.1\n|14\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Hale County, Alabama|Hale]]\n|3\n|15,760\n|19\n|643.9\n|24\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Henry County, Alabama|Henry]]\n|3\n|17,302\n|17\n|561.8\n|31\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Houston County, Alabama|Houston]]\n|19\n|101,547\n|19\n|579.8\n|175\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Jackson County, Alabama|Jackson]]\n|14\n|53,227\n|26\n|1,077.9\n|49\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Jefferson County, Alabama|Jefferson]]\n|416\n|658,466\n|63\n|1,111.3\n|593\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Lamar County, Alabama|Lamar]]\n|3\n|14,564\n|21\n|604.9\n|24\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Lauderdale County, Alabama|Lauderdale]]\n|16\n|92,709\n|17\n|667.7\n|139\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Lawrence County, Alabama|Lawrence]]\n|6\n|34,339\n|17\n|690.7\n|50\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Lee County, Alabama|Lee]]\n|110\n|140,247\n|78\n|607.5\n|231\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Limestone County, Alabama|Limestone]]\n|32\n|82,782\n|39\n|559.9\n|148\